Program: Outlook
Title: Imprisoned by My Father for 15 Years
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3csvqp9
Last Broadcast Date: Wed 17 Jan 2018
Psychotherapist Maude Julien grew up in what she calls a 'cult of three' in France and was put through extreme tests by her father. She tells Jo Fidgen how she overcame the ordeal. Carla Valentine from the UK runs a dating website for morticians, embalmers and funeral directors. Outlook's Saskia Edwards went to meet her. Rachel DeWoskin is the American star of a hit Chinese soap opera. She discusses how she became an accidental celebrity in a foreign country. (Picture: Maude Julien. Photo credit: Alain Schmidt.) Show less